<HEADLINE>
<P>
BUSIEST HARBOR? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The story "Harboring Taste for a Quick Cruise," by Bill Hughes (Sept. 24) 
states that it "provides an enjoyable narrated cruise on the world's busiest 
harbor." Interesting article, but since when is Los Angeles the busiest harbor 
in the world? 
</P>
<P>
PETER HUME 
</P>
<P>
El Toro 
</P>
