<P>
15 KILLED AS BUSES COLLIDE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
ILIGAN, Philippines 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Fifteen people were killed and 28 wounded when two buses collided Saturday at a 
blind curve along a main highway in the southern Philippines, a military 
spokesman said. 
</P>
</TEXT>
