<HEADLINE>
<P>
A 'THANKS' FOR DOUG 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Driving down Laguna Canyon Road recently, my car ran out of gas in the middle 
of nowhere. I was there all alone. After sitting in my car for what seemed like 
forever, I decided to walk before it got too late. I heard something rolling 
over the pebbles behind me, and there was a man sitting on a bike. He rode to a 
phone, and in 30 minutes my family was there to get me. 
</P>
<P>
All I know about the man is that his name is Doug. I would like to say thank 
you. 
</P>
<P>
METER JONES 
</P>
<P>
Orange 
</P>
