JAZZ; MONK, THELONIOUS; ZWERIN, CHARLOTTE; RICKER, BRUCE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA111989-0124 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 137064 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
November 19, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
