CATTLE; SHEEP; MEAT; LIVESTOCK; ANIMAL LIBERATION FRONT; EARTH FIRST 
(ORGANIZATION); ENVIRONMENTALISTS; VEGETARIANS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
