SEARS ROEBUCK AND CO; IMPORT FEES; TELEVISION SETS; DUMPING (TRADE); UNITED 
STATES -- TRADE -- JAPAN; REAL, MANUEL L; MILLER, STEPHEN D; GORMAN, PAUL G 
(ATTORNEY) 
</P>
