HARASSMENT; DEMONSTRATIONS -- LOS ANGELES; BEAUTIFICATION; MORE ADVOCATES FOR 
SAFE HOMES (ORGANIZATION); PUBLIC SAFETY; VOLUNTEERS; CRIME PREVENTION 
</P>
