carrying 112 pounds, finished a head in front of Bookkeeper, ridden by Santos 
and carrying 113 pounds. Why Go On Dreaming was another neck back. 
</P>
<P>
Rootentootenwooten went 1 1/8 miles on the fast track in 1:51 3/5, earning 
$109,440 with her second win in six career starts. She returned $24.60, $8.20 
and $3.60. 
