<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski recorded a $79 profit Saturday when one of his 
$10 exacta boxes, Silver Hatchet and Best Picture in the third race hit for a 
$21.80 payoff for $2. The profit pushed Mieszerski back into the profit column. 
He started the meeting Wednesday with a mythical bankroll of $1,000 which now 
stands at $1,077. 
</P>
<P>
Each racing day Bob will make at least one bet. He could make a straight win 
bet, he could make a daily double bet, he could make an exacta bet, he could 
make other exotic bets, or any combination of bets. But, he will make at least 
one bet. 
</P>
<P>
For today, Bob's bets are $10 daily triples from Defend Your Man in the fourth 
to Keen Night, Naturally Mitch, Rusty Attitude and His Legacy in the fifth to 
Sun Streak in the sixth. 
</P>
<P>
</P>
<P>
Beginning Bankroll: $1,000 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Profit: $79 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll: $1,077 
</P>
